        public static int[] randomListWithRange(int min,

                                        int number)
        A method that generates a list of a certain amount of random numbers between min and max. It also makes sure that none of the number repeat.
        Parameters:

        max - The maximum value that can be generated.
        number - The amount of numbers that should be generated.
